{"kind": "text", "text": ")"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "with his hind feet;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, K;) like"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Aisotan~a", "text_ar": "اِسْتَنَّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; (S;) as also ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qm~S", "text_ar": "قمّص", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": (A:) or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qumaASN", "text_ar": "قُمَاصٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", with damm,"}, {"kind": "page_break", "n": 2564}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is the inf. n. when it signifies he did so usually: (K:) and, inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qimaASN", "text_ar": "قِمَاصٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qumaASN", "text_ar": "قُمَاصٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ","}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he pranced, leaped, sprang,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "bounded:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(M, K:) and, inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qimaASN", "text_ar": "قِمَاصٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he was,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "became, restless, unquiet,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "unsteady,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K, TA,)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "and took fright, and ran away at random,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "shied:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA:) and, inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qumaASN", "text_ar": "قُمَاصٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "it"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(a bird of the kind called"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "nugar", "text_ar": "نُغَر"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ")"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "remained not steadily in a place, but leaped from its place impatiently:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and, inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qamoSN", "text_ar": "قَمْصٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he took fright, and ran away at random,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "shied, and turned aside"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "away."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) You say,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "h`*ihi Ald~aAb~apu fiyhaA qimaASN", "text_ar": "هٰذِهِ الدَّابَّةُ فِيهَا قِمَاصٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; you should not say"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qumaASN", "text_ar": "قُمَاصٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; (S;) or you say"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qumaASN", "text_ar": "قُمَاصٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "also; (TA;) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qamaASN", "text_ar": "قَمَاصٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", which last is the most chaste; (L, TA;)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "This beast has in her a property of raising and putting down her fore legs together, and beating the ground with her hind legs."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S.) And it is said in a proverb, (S,)"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "maA biAlEayori mino qimaASK", "text_ar": "مَا بِالعَيْرِ مِنْ قِمَاصٍ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (S, A, K,) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qumaASK", "text_ar": "قُمَاصٍ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; (Sgh, TA; and so, as well as"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qimaASK", "text_ar": "قِمَاصٍ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", in two copies of the S;) i. e."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlHimaAr", "text_ar": "الحِمَار"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; (S;) ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "There is not in the ass any power of raising and putting down his fore legs together,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c.;] applied to him who has become low, or mean, after being high, in rank, or condition; (S, A, K;) and to a weak man, in whom is no activity: (A, K:) or, as the proverb is related by Sb,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^afalaA qumaASa biAlEayori", "text_ar": "اَفَلَا قُمَاصَ بِالعَيْرِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Is there not, then, any power"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c."}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in the ass?"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "] (M, TA.) And in a trad.,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "faqamaSato bihi faSaraEatohu", "text_ar": "فَقَمَصَتْ بِهِ فَصَرَعَتْهُ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "And it leaped,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "sprang,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "bounded, and took fright, and ran away at random,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "shied, with him, and threw him down."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) You also say,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Aln~aAqapu biAlr~adiyfi", "text_ar": "النَّاقَةُ بِالرَّدِيفِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qam~aSati", "text_ar": "قَمَّصَتِ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The she-camel went briskly with the rider upon the hinder part."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qamaSa AlbaHoru biAls~afiynapi", "text_ar": "قَمَصَ البَحْرُ بِالسَّفِينَةِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (S, K,) or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "bihaA", "text_ar": "بِهَا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qam~aSa", "text_ar": "قَمَّصَ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (A,) (tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The sea put the ship in a state of commotion"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, A, K)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "by the waves"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, A)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "thereof."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A.) And it is said in a trad.,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "lataqomiSan~a bikumu AlA^aroDu qumaASa Aln~ugari", "text_ar": "لَتَقْمِصَنَّ بِكُمُ الاَرْضُ قُمَاصَ النُّغَرِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Verily the earth shall be in a state of commotion with you"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "like the commotion of the"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "kind of bird called"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "ngr", "text_ar": "نغر"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (TA.) You say also,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^axa*ahu AlqimaASu", "text_ar": "اَخَذَهُ القِمَاصُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Restlessness,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "inquietude,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "unsteadiness, seized him."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A, TA.) And, of a horse whose sciatic vein or nerve is contracted, ("}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "$anija", "text_ar": "شَنِجَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", [not"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "$bH", "text_ar": "شبح"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "as in Freytag's Lexicon,])"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "qamaSato rijolupu", "text_ar": "قَمَصَتْ رِجْلُةُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[app. meaning,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "His hind leg became twitched up,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "as in springhalt]: in which case you also say of him,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlEuroquwbi", "text_ar": "العُرْقُوبِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_in~ahu laqaAmiSu", "text_ar": "اـِنَّهُ لَقَامِصُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[as though meaning,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "verily he has a twitching up of the hock"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (S, TA.) [See also"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "EusaAfN", "text_ar": "عُسَافٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".]"}], "source_refs": ["S", "M", "A", "Msb", "K", "TA"]}]}, "classical_definitions": null, "translations_attribution": {"model": "qwen36-35b-heretic", "generated_date": "2026-05-18", "